{"data":{"page":{"html":"<h1 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Options</h1>\n<div class=\"toc\">\n<h2><a href=\"#toc\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Table of Contents</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#global-options\">Global options</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#usage\">Usage</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#available-actions\">Available actions</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p>Options is a plain JavaScript object used to contextualise the execution of an action.</p>\n<h2 id=\"global-options\"><a href=\"#global-options\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Global options</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/options/attempt/\"><code class=\"language-text\">attempt</code></a> (number, readonly, 0)\nIndicates the number of times an action has been rescheduled for execution when an error occurred. </li>\n<li><a href=\"/options/cascade/\"><code class=\"language-text\">cascade</code></a> (object|array, optional)<br>\nPropagates an option and its value to every child actions.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/options/debug/\"><code class=\"language-text\">debug</code></a> (boolean, optional, false)<br>\nPrint detailed logs to the standard error output (<code class=\"language-text\">stderr</code>).</li>\n<li><a href=\"/options/handler/\"><code class=\"language-text\">handler</code></a> (function, required)<br>\nDefine the function that an action implements to get things done.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/options/header/\"><code class=\"language-text\">header</code></a> (string, optional)<br>\nTitle of an actions or of a group of actions.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/options/once/\"><code class=\"language-text\">once</code></a> (boolean|array|string, optional, false)<br>\nEnsure that the same actions are only executed once.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/options/relax/\"><code class=\"language-text\">relax</code></a> (boolean, optional, false)<br>\nMakes an action tolerant to internal errors.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/options/retry/\"><code class=\"language-text\">retry</code></a> (number|boolean, optional, 1)<br>\nControl over how many time an action is re-scheduled on error before it is finally treated as a failure.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/options/shy/\"><code class=\"language-text\">shy</code></a> (boolean, optional, false)<br>\nDisables the modification of the session status.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/options/sleep/\"><code class=\"language-text\">sleep</code></a> (number, optional, 3000)<br>\nTime lapse when a failed action is rescheduled.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/options/sudo/\"><code class=\"language-text\">sudo</code></a> (boolean, optional, false)<br>\nEscalates the right of the current user with <code class=\"language-text\">root</code> privileges.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage</h2>\n<p>Creating an option is as easy as passing one or multiple objects when calling an action:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'nikita'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">call</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>my_key<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'with a value'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">assert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>options<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>my_key<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'with a value'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"available-actions\"><a href=\"#available-actions\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Available actions</h2>\n<p>Each actions in Nikita expect specific options. You must consult the documentation of each individual actions to know in detail which options are available.</p>\n<p>Some actions are globally available to every actions. They are defined and managed by Nikita itself. You can consult the documentation of each option to obtain detailed information about its usage and behaviour.</p>","fields":{"slug":"/options/","edit_url":"https://github.com/adaltas/node-nikita-docs/edit/master/src/md/options.md"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Options","description":null,"keywords":null}}},"pageContext":{}}